reviews.review_text:
The best show... .. I don't remember.

I remember leaving Foxboro, I remember we went to Buffahole - we were hooking up with friends, I once lived there. I remember the trip from Buffalo to Vermont, through the north country back roads.  I really just don't remember this show.

I'd give this show a 5 trips out of 5, except the transition from Gimme Some Lovin' to Wharf Rat is  a stumble and the transition from Around and Around to Sunshine Daydream just isn't. 

I'd be disappointed in the BD encore, especially after the 2 hours before, except it is the 2nd best I ever heard.

Overall, one of the BEST FUCKIN' SHOWS ... EVER. and even more so considering Brent a month or so later.
Year of the Spotted Moon Great stuff as it does by ~
